cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC. 

The paper deals with the problem of answer ranking in community Question Answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also incorporates rich syntactic and semantic embeddings, which suggests relevance to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of neural networks for modeling complex non-linear interactions points towards Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-categories as well.
